en completed-103</a></td><td>Second mumps dose from the primary series was administered. The primary series has been completed</td><td><div><p>\"Completed the primary vaccination series\" = TRUE (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Mumps-containing vaccines\")\"</p>\n</div></td></tr></table></div>"
